{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/roberto-silvosa/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"21874f47-feda-5ab7-a12e-6e26dce57db1","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/robertosilvosa/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived template</a></p>\n<p>Roberto Silvosa contacted me to design and build a custom website for his business with an special emphasis on the aesthetics. He also needed to be able to upload new photos of his floral projects.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 101%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/87c0f4798ee5faedebe84fdaaaab0f8c/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>The portfolio of works uses a book metaphor to swipe the photos, which are loaded from the custom CMS built for the Flash website. It also has a small product catalog and checkout system to allow customers to order products via email. The products in the catalog and the news are also controlled via CMS.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\